{"word":"ἀνεπιτήδειος","slug":"ἀνεπιτήδειος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀνεπιτήδειος</b></el> <p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>unserviceable, unfit</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>:— <i>mischievous, prejudicial, hurtful</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>unkind, unfriendly</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}